addAgreement(address).details: Add an agreement to the whitelist

isAgreementListed(address).details: Check if the agreement is whitelisted

isOwner().details: Returns true if the caller is the current owner.

mapAgreements(uint256).details: Map list of the agreements using a bitmap

maskAgreementBit(uint256,address).details: Create a new bitmask by adding agreement class to it.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. unmaskAgreementBit(uint256,address).details: Create a new bitmask by removing agreement class from it.
